Budget Controller Dashboard. Four Panels: 1) Global Budget: Daily Limit 100 EUR, Spent 67 EUR (67%), Progress Bar, Alert at 80%. 2) User Budget: Per User 5 EUR/day, Top 5 Spenders table. 3) Rate Limit: 60 req/min per User, Current Usage gauge. 4) Request Flow: Check Request (Estimated Cost) -> Global Budget? -> User Budget? -> Rate Limit? -> Allow/Deny -> Record Actual Cost. Flow diagram with decision diamonds. German labels.